text: Albert Victor Hyzler (20 November 1916 - 26 October 1993)https://www.timesofmalta.com/mobile/articles/view/20161124/opinion/MP- for-three-parties.631900 was a Maltese politician. He was the Acting President of Malta from 27 December 1981 to 15 February 1982. ==References== Category:1916 births Category:1993 deaths Category:Presidents of Malta
